WITH two_year_deaths AS (
    SELECT
        d.diagnosisname,
        COUNT(CASE WHEN p.hospitaldischargestatus = 'expired' AND p.hospitaldischargetime <= DATETIME(p.unitadmittime, '+2 years') THEN 1 END) AS deaths_within_2_years,
        COUNT(DISTINCT d.patientunitstayid) AS total_cases
    FROM
        diagnosis d
    JOIN
        patient p ON d.patientunitstayid = p.patientunitstayid
    GROUP BY
        d.diagnosisname
),
mortality_rate AS (
    SELECT
        diagnosisname,
        (CAST(deaths_within_2_years AS FLOAT) / total_cases) * 100 AS mortality_rate
    FROM
        two_year_deaths
)
SELECT 
    diagnosisname, 
    mortality_rate
FROM 
    mortality_rate
ORDER BY 
    mortality_rate DESC
LIMIT 3;

        patientunitstayid,
        MIN(intakeoutputtime) AS first_feed_time
    FROM

        celllabel = 'enteral formula'
    GROUP BY
        patientunitstayid
),
BronchodilatorPatients AS (
    SELECT
        m.patientunitstayid,
        m.drugname,
        MIN(m.drugstarttime) AS first_bronchodilator_time
    FROM
        medication m
    WHERE
        m.drugname LIKE '%bronchodilator - beta-agonist%'
    GROUP BY
        m.patientunitstayid, m.drugname
),
PatientsDuringSameMonth AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT
        f.patientunitstayid
    FROM
        FirstEnteralFeed f
    JOIN BronchodilatorPatients b ON f.patientunitstayid = b.patientunitstayid
    WHERE
        STRFTIME('%Y-%m', b.first_bronchodilator_time) = STRFTIME('%Y-%m', f.first_feed_time)
        AND f.first_feed_time >= '2104-12-31 23:59:00'
)
SELECT
    COUNT(*) AS patient_count
FROM
    PatientsDuringSameMonth;

    COUNT(t.treatmentid) AS procedure_count
FROM 
    treatment t
JOIN 
    lab l ON t.patientunitstayid = l.patientunitstayid
JOIN 
    patient p ON t.patientunitstayid = p.patientunitstayid
WHERE 
    l.labname = 'oxygen therapy' 
    AND l.labresult BETWEEN 40 AND 60
    AND l.labresulttime >= DATETIME(p.hospitaladmittime, '-1 YEAR') 
    AND l.labresulttime < p.hospitaladmittime
GROUP BY 
    t.treatmentname
ORDER BY 
    procedure_count DESC
LIMIT 4;
